@host = http://localhost:5279
@tenant = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@user = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002
@token = reemplazar_con_access_token

### Registro (crea tenant + usuario admin)
POST {{host}}/api/Auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@empresa.com",
  "password": "Password1!",
  "tenantName": "Mi imprenta"
}

### Login (con DeviceControl.Enabled=true añade deviceId)
POST {{host}}/api/Auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@empresa.com",
  "password": "Password1!",
  "deviceId": "mi-app-ios-uuid-o-stable-id",
  "deviceName": "iPhone de Ana"
}

### Items (requiere Authorization: Bearer + X-Device-Id si DeviceControl está activo)
GET {{host}}/api/Items
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Device-Id: mi-app-ios-uuid-o-stable-id

### Compat: Items con cabeceras (sin JWT) — el endpoint sigue exigiendo autenticación; usa token o ajusta política
# GET {{host}}/api/Items
# X-Tenant-Id: {{tenant}}

### Control remoto / kill switch (sin JWT ni X-Tenant-Id)
GET {{host}}/api/app-config

### Con versión (query)
GET {{host}}/api/app-config?version=1.2.0

### Con versión (cabecera)
GET {{host}}/api/app-config
X-App-Version: 1.2.0

### Ejemplo de cálculo (público)
GET {{host}}/api/CalculationExample
Accept: application/json

### Ejemplo pipeline flexible (público)
GET {{host}}/api/CalculationExample/flexible
Accept: application/json

### Motor flexible: activar por tenant
PUT {{host}}/api/PricingSettings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "flexiblePricingEnabled": true
}

### Listar reglas (orden SortOrder)
GET {{host}}/api/PricingRules
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Crear regla: margen 30%
POST {{host}}/api/PricingRules
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Margen 30",
  "type": "Percentage",
  "value": 30,
  "sortOrder": 0
}

### Crear regla: fórmula (costo*1.5+200 es ilustrativo; en servicios reales material suele ser el costo unitario)
POST {{host}}/api/PricingRules
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ajuste fórmula",
  "type": "Formula",
  "expression": "material * 1.5 + 0.2 * qty",
  "sortOrder": 10
}

###
